    <item>
      <title>里夫斯表示，英国的规划决策“不可能总是否定的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/reeves-says-answer-can-t-always-be-no-on-britain-s-planning-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯表示，在批准重大基础设施工程和规划决策时“答案不能总是否定的”，这是她将推进有争议的项目以促进英国经济发展的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/reeves-says-answer-can-t-always-be-no-on-britain-s-planning-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 07:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库基斯称，欧盟应在对关税采取报复性措施之前与美国进行对话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/eu-should-talk-to-us-before-retaliating-on-tariffs-kukies-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长约尔格·库基斯表示，如果欧盟与美国就潜在的贸易关税进行谈判，而不是立即采取反制措施，欧盟可能会处于更有利的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/eu-should-talk-to-us-before-retaliating-on-tariffs-kukies-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 07:01:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪考虑降低关税、增加进口以应对特朗普威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/modi-mulls-lower-tariffs-more-imports-to-counter-trump-s-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果美国总统唐纳德·特朗普采取威胁的贸易行动，印度政府正在评估包括贸易协议、削减关税和从美国进口更多商品等多种选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/modi-mulls-lower-tariffs-more-imports-to-counter-trump-s-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 06:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪的关键盟友将在美国调查结束后对阿达尼采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/modi-s-key-ally-to-act-on-adani-only-after-us-probe-concludes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的最大盟友表示，他将等待美国检察机关对亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼贿赂指控的调查结束，然后再采取任何行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/modi-s-key-ally-to-act-on-adani-only-after-us-probe-concludes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 05:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼通过盈利规则向大宗商品公司施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/indonesia-s-tougher-fx-lock-up-adds-pressure-on-commodity-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼计划强制大宗商品企业将出口收入留在国内至少一年，此举将进一步收紧现有要求，因为该行业已经面临越来越多监管不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/indonesia-s-tougher-fx-lock-up-adds-pressure-on-commodity-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 02:34:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日美同意将关系推向新高度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/japan-s-iwaya-us-s-rubio-agree-on-bringing-ties-to-new-heights</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本外务大臣岩屋毅表示，他和美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥在首次会晤中同意将两国关系推向新的高度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/japan-s-iwaya-us-s-rubio-agree-on-bringing-ties-to-new-heights</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 01:03:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上任第二天扩大对中国和欧洲的关税威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-says-he-s-still-weighing-10-tariff-threat-on-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统上任第一天就将关税威胁扩大到中国和欧盟，而上任第二天他的目标就包括加拿大和墨西哥。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-says-he-s-still-weighing-10-tariff-threat-on-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 00:04:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南与特朗普通话并致力于高尔夫外交</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/vietnam-spoke-with-trump-and-is-working-on-its-golf-diplomacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南总理范明政表示，越南最高领导人最近与唐纳德·特朗普进行了交谈，并准备好与美国新总统及其政府打交道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/vietnam-spoke-with-trump-and-is-working-on-its-golf-diplomacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 17:39:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将接受 18,000 名美国公民以安抚特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/india-set-to-take-back-18-000-citizens-from-us-to-placate-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府准备与唐纳德·特朗普政府合作，识别并接回所有非法居住在美国的印度公民，这是新德里方面愿意遵守新任美国总统的规定并避免贸易战的早期信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/india-set-to-take-back-18-000-citizens-from-us-to-placate-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:02:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
